"{\"uid\": \"thenews.com.pk-latest-1214853-bella-hadid-regrets-doing-adidas-munich-olympics-themed-campaign\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Bella Hadid is \\\"upset\\\" with her \\\"recent campaign with adidas.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 62, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bella Hadid\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid opened up on the recent controversial Adidas SL72 campaign that referenced the 1972 Munich Olympics, which has a \\\"horrific tragedy\\\" linked to itself.\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 108, \"end\": 114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.689880179631379e-17, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}, {\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"score\": 0.9999999999588454, \"rank\": 4.125288757945846e-11, \"text\": \"1972 Munich Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For those of you who do not know my heart, I want to make sure you are hearing directly from me about my recent campaign with adidas,\\\" the 27-year-old supermodel began a message shared on her Instagram stories.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.930978318485992e-14, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid clarified that she \\\"would never knowingly engage with any art or work that is linked to a horrific tragedy of any kind.\\\"\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In advance of the campaign's release, I had no knowledge of the historical connection to the atrocious events in 1972.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am shocked, I am upset, and I am disappointed in the lack of sensitivity that went into this campaign.\\\"\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In celebration of the 52nd anniversary of the Munich Olympics, Adidas released an advertisement earlier this month that featured Hadid clutching a \\\"coveted classic\\\" trainer from the 1970s.\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"score\": 0.9999999999838565, \"rank\": 1.623064429355582e-11, \"text\": \"Munich Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich_massacre\"}, {\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.689880179631379e-17, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During those summer games, an extremist group assassinated 11 Israeli athletes and one German police officer, leaving an unforgettable tragedy behind.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.8704799605220068, \"rank\": 0.14661191099777435, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\"}, {\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9070575524038752, \"rank\": 0.10244702136490952, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Had I been made aware, from the bottom of my heart, I would never have participated,\\\" Bella further explained.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 0.9999999999924967, \"rank\": 7.466023058793739e-12, \"text\": \"Bella\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My team should have known, adidas should have known and I should have done more research so that I too would have known and understood, and spoken up.\\\"\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The model committed that she \\\"will always speak up for what I believe to be wrong.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While everyone's intentions were to make something positive, and bring people together through art, the collective lack of understanding from all parties undermined the process.\\\"\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not believe in hate in any form, including antisemitism,\\\" Hadid declared, adding, \\\"That will never waiver, and I stand by that statement to the fullest extent.\\\"\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Connecting the liberation of the Palestinian people to an attack so tragic, is something that hurts my heart,\\\" the pro-Palestinian shared.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1863, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Palestinian people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Palestine is not synonymous with terrorism and this campaign unintentionally highlighted an event that does not present who we are.\\\"\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9997734771244888, \"rank\": 0.00022575776587502344, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bella embraced being a \\\"proud Palestinian woman\\\" and expressed \\\"there is much more to our culture than the things that have been equated over the past week.\\\"\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2105, \"end\": 2110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 0.9999999999924967, \"rank\": 7.466023058793739e-12, \"text\": \"Bella\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}, {\"begin\": 2135, \"end\": 2146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9632161516523885, \"rank\": 0.03469572517490866, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will forever stand by my people of Palestine while continuing to advocate for a world free of antisemitism.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2302, \"end\": 2311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9997734771244888, \"rank\": 0.00022575776587502344, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Antisemitism has no place in the liberation of the Palestinian people.\\\"\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2426, \"end\": 2444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Palestinian people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Towards conclusion, the model wrote, \\\"I will always stand for peace over violence, any day.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hate has no place here, and I will forever advocate for not only my people, but every person world wide.\\\"\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The News International, All Rights Reserved\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2665, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The News International\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_News_International\"}]}]}"